@baseUrl=http://localhost:8080/api/members

### member list
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?isActive=true

### search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?isActive=0

### search
# []
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?isActive=1&bloodType=B

### search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?nickname=hong

### search
# "datetime": "유효하지 않은 날짜 형식(yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm)입니다."
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?datetime=2026-03-05 16:01:26

### search
# "datetime": "유효하지 않은 날짜 형식(yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm)입니다."
